g.text: Customer segmentation is the sub-division of a market into discrete different groups of customers, where each group shares similar characteristics. This workflow illustrates how to build a basic
customer segmentation model, using a clustering procedure.
Build a basic customer segmentation using a clustering procedure.

Learner nodes output a PMML model (blue square output port).
